the factors is p minus n.

00:00:40.858 --> 00:00:45.666
So this could be factored as p plus n,

00:00:46.366 --> 00:00:47.879
times p minus n.

00:00:47.879 --> 00:00:50.673
This is just factoring
a difference of squares,

00:00:50.673 --> 00:00:52.776
is equal to 12.

