00:01:15.842 --> 00:01:17.900
So this is going to be a positive value.

00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:19.966
So let's think about all
the different combinations

00:01:19.966 --> 00:01:22.900
of positive integers that
we could take their product

00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:24.900
